Embeddings¶

These embeddings have been trained for 1, 2, 4, and 8 epochs, possibly leading to representations with varying amounts of noise, or even differences in the structure of latent semantic dimensions.

In [7]:
# import module to handle word vectors
from subs2vec.vecs import Vectors

# load vectors
n = 2e4  # set number of word vectors to load
d = 300 # set dimensionality
epoch1 = Vectors('subs.epoch1.en.vec', normalize=True, n=n, d=d)
epoch2 = Vectors('subs.epoch2.en.vec', normalize=True, n=n, d=d)
epoch4 = Vectors('subs.epoch4.en.vec', normalize=True, n=n, d=d)
epoch8 = Vectors('subs.epoch8.en.vec', normalize=True, n=n, d=d)
